WEBVTT

00:07:58.564 --> 00:08:00.058
just for a day.

00:08:00.082 --> 00:08:01.563
And if this sounds easy,

00:08:01.587 --> 00:08:02.836
you haven't tried it.

00:08:02.860 --> 00:08:04.920
Here's listener Amanda Itzko.

00:08:04.944 --> 00:08:08.684
(Audio) Amanda Itzko:
I am absolutely itching.

00:08:08.708 --> 00:08:11.164
I feel a little bit crazy,

00:08:11.188 --> 00:08:15.872
because I have noticed
that I pick up my phone

00:08:15.896 --> 00:08:19.804
when I'm just walking
from one room to another,

00:08:19.828 --> 00:08:21.094
getting on the elevator,

00:08:21.118 --> 00:08:24.895
and even -- and this is the part
that I am really embarrassed

00:08:24.919 --> 00:08:26.906
to actually say out loud --

00:08:26.930 --> 00:08:28.357
in the car.

00:08:28.381 --> 00:08:29.554
MZ: Yikes.

00:08:29.578 --> 00:08:31.247
Yeah, well, but as Amanda learned,